1:21:17.247 --> 1:21:18.665
Nice punch, Gary.

1:21:18.749 --> 1:21:21.460
Yeah, you really laid out
that very tiny woman.

1:21:21.543 --> 1:21:23.420
Maybe take it easy on the old ladies, huh?

1:21:23.504 --> 1:21:25.589
- Big Guy might be watching.
- Come on, guys.

1:21:25.672 --> 1:21:27.424
[screams]

1:21:28.926 --> 1:21:30.135
[all exclaim]

1:21:31.387 --> 1:21:32.513
Or not.

1:21:39.520 --> 1:21:40.604
Guys.

1:21:41.271 --> 1:21:44.900
[chanting]

1:21:53.575 --> 1:21:55.619
The time is close, my son.

1:21:56.662 --> 1:21:58.497
Yours is the greatest sacrifice.

1:21:59.498 --> 1:22:00.332
[grunts]

1:22:00.416 --> 1:22:02.626
You are but a vessel for greatness!

1:22:02.709 --> 1:22:03.544
[grunts]

1:22:03.627 --> 1:22:07.047
[chanting] Kill the child!
Kill the child! Kill the child!

1:22:07.131 --> 1:22:09.550
Kill the child! Kill the child!

1:22:09.633 --> 1:22:11.885
