- Right.

1:22:40.622 --> 1:22:41.957
The time has come!

1:22:42.040 --> 1:22:44.918
- Ten, nine, eight...
- They're gonna kill him, Gar!

1:22:45.002 --> 1:22:46.879
- Seven, six.
- Heads up.

1:22:46.962 --> 1:22:48.839
Five, four...

1:22:48.922 --> 1:22:51.925
- It's all up to you now, buddy.
- Three, two, one!

1:22:52.009 --> 1:22:54.511
The time has come
to open the gates of hell!

1:22:54.595 --> 1:22:56.180
[cheering]

1:22:56.263 --> 1:22:57.681
Gary, now!

1:23:01.727 --> 1:23:02.727
[grunts]

1:23:04.688 --> 1:23:06.523
