1:23:39.431 --> 1:23:40.474
Oh, shit.

1:23:40.557 --> 1:23:43.143
"to... be...?"

1:23:44.019 --> 1:23:45.145
Oh, shit.

1:23:45.854 --> 1:23:47.397
Hey, Lucas?

1:23:48.440 --> 1:23:49.691
You okay, buddy?

1:23:52.653 --> 1:23:54.321
[demonic growl]

1:23:54.905 --> 1:23:56.865
[all exclaiming]

1:24:07.876 --> 1:24:09.169
Lucas!

1:24:09.670 --> 1:24:10.670
[Gary] Lucas!

1:24:12.172 --> 1:24:13.172
Lucas!

1:24:14.841 --> 1:24:15.926
[grunts]

1:24:19.096 --> 1:24:21.139
I got you, buddy! I got you!

1:24:22.391 --> 1:24:24.226
[demonic voice] Let me go!

1:24:24.309 --> 1:24:27.020
- No!
- You must let me go!

1:24:27.104 --> 1:24:28.897
No! I won't!

1:24:31.567 --> 1:24:33.735
- [normal voice] Daddy?
- Yes, Lucas?

1:24:34.861 --> 1:24:36.071
I'm scared.

1:24:36.738 --> 1:24:38.156
Don't be scared, sweetie.

1:24:39.241 --> 1:24:43.704
- I got you.
- [demonic voice] Let him go!

1:24:47.040 --> 1:24:49.543
[screaming]

1:24:51.628 --> 1:24:54.840
Okay, maybe a little fear
is totally justified,

1:24:54.923 --> 1:24:56.550
but I'm not letting you go!

1:24:56.633 --> 1:24:58.010
I'm never letting go, buddy!

1:24:58.093 --> 1:25:01.096
- Why?
- Because I'm your father!

1:25:01.179 --> 1:25:02.723
And I love you!

1:25:02.806 --> 1:25:05.684
[demonic voice] You're his stepfather!

1:25:05.767 --> 1:25:07.853
[screaming]

1:25:15.569 --> 1:25:16.862
I'm not leaving you!

1:25:25.037 --> 1:25:27.789
[groaning]

1:25:27.873 --> 1:25:29.166
Fuck!

1:25:30.542 --> 1:25:31.710
- Oh, my God.
- [coughing]

1:25:31.793 --> 1:25:33.545
- You okay?
- Yeah.

1:25:34.421 --> 1:25:35.881
- Gary.
- Gary.

1:25:42.346 --> 1:25:43.346
Lucas!

1:25:45.098 --> 1:25:46.141
Gary!

1:25:48.977 --> 1:25:51.730
- I'm sorry.
- I'm so sorry.

1:25:55.901 --> 1:25:57.069
[Samantha crying]

1:26:00.530 --> 1:26:01.530
Oh, my God!

1:26:01.573 --> 1:26:03.617
[overlapping chatter]

1:26:03.700 --> 1:26:05.077
- Help him up!
- Come on.

1:26:05.160 --> 1:26:06.578
- Easy.
- All right.

1:26:10.415 --> 1:26:11.541
Let him breathe.

1:26:11.625 --> 1:26:13.919
That's some Indiana Jones shit, dawg.

1:26:14.419 --> 1:26:17.297
Holy shit. Oh, my God.

1:26:17.381 --> 1:26:20.008
He's probably got minor scrapes,
but you know...

1:26:20.467 --> 1:26:23.053
- It's 'cause of us. It's 'cause of us.
- We did good.

1:26:23.136 --> 1:26:27.099
Hon, you told me when you're a parent,
you hope for the best,

1:26:27.182 --> 1:26:28.475
but prepare for the worst.

1:26:28.558 --> 1:26:30.727
- Yeah.
- Please tell me that was it.

1:26:30.811 --> 1:26:32.020
[laughs]

1:26:32.104 --> 1:26:34.064
You did it. [chuckles]

1:26:34.147 --> 1:26:35.941
You really came through for us.

1:26:36.775 --> 1:26:38.026
You're the one, baby.

1:26:38.735 --> 1:26:40.028
You were always the one.

1:26:40.612 --> 1:26:41.697
I love you.

1:26:42.489 --> 1:26:43.489
[grunts]

1:26:45.867 --> 1:26:47.035
I love you, too.

