- Come on.

1:27:02.801 --> 1:27:04.553
[shouts]

1:27:04.636 --> 1:27:06.304
[all grunting]

1:27:06.388 --> 1:27:09.099
- [screaming]
- Oh, shit!

1:27:09.558 --> 1:27:11.852
